      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REARRANGED (8) produced a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 340m behind Narrow Arrow (19.92). Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can atone. QUEEN CANICULA (1) turned in a better effort at Richmond last start, finishing second behind SCOTT LOTTIE (18.76) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. TIP ME FRANK (4) steps out at this track for the first time after an average run at the latest appearance, finishing fourth at Nowra over 365m behind Lollipop Ethics (21.31). Can figure in the finish. WINSOME TEARS (5) collected a minor prize last start and must be considered.",
